---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">

  <Header />

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10">Services</h1>

    <!-- Core support -->
    <div class="mb-10 p-6 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">🛠️ IT Support & Troubleshooting</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Day-to-day IT support, fixing issues quickly and keeping systems running. Most work starts here — something isn’t working, or things just need to be set up properly.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Website and hosting issues</li>
        <li>Email, domains and DNS problems</li>
        <li>General troubleshooting and system fixes</li>
        <li>Ongoing maintenance and support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Cloud & SaaS -->
    <div class="mb-10 p-6 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">☁️ Cloud, SaaS & Infrastructure</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Setup, migration and support across modern cloud platforms and SaaS tools. Not sold as products — just implemented properly.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Microsoft 365 & Google Workspace</li>
        <li>Email migrations and setup</li>
        <li>AWS, Azure, GCP and Cloudways</li>
        <li>Backup (Backblaze) and endpoint security (ESET)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Networking -->
    <div class="mb-10 p-6 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">🌐 Networking & Infrastructure</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Reliable, properly configured networks — from small office setups to more complex environments.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Network setup and optimisation</li>
        <li>WiFi and connectivity issues</li>
        <li>UniFi and similar systems</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Databases -->
    <div class="mb-10 p-6 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">🗄️ Databases & Development</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Practical database work — both support and development — across a range of platforms.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>SQL Server, MySQL, PostgreSQL</li>
        <li>Snowflake and data platforms</li>
        <li>Query optimisation and troubleshooting</li>
        <li>Custom development and integrations</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Web & Ecommerce -->
    <div class="mb-10 p-6 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">🛒 Web & E-commerce</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Websites and online stores that work properly, and don’t become a maintenance headache.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>WordPress builds and fixes</li>
        <li>Shopify, EKM and OpenCart</li>
        <li>Hosting, performance and stability</li>
        <li>Integrations and custom functionality</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Projects -->
    <div class="mb-10 p-6 border rounded-xl hover:shadow-sm transition">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">🚀 Projects & Consultancy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        From one-off fixes to larger projects — including multi-site builds and system overhauls. If it’s not something I handle directly, I’ll bring in the right people and manage it properly.
      </p>
    </div>
<div class="mt-16 p-6 border rounded-xl">
  <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Not sure what you need?</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
    If something isn’t working or you just want a second opinion, get in touch and we can have a quick chat.
  </p>
  <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
    Contact me →
  </a>
</div>
  </section>

</Layout>